; Intentional GREYBOX PLACEHOLDER (2026-06-21 art refactor). All painterly art
; (clockwork world-kits, island/beacon GLBs, fx, sky shader, audio scenes) is
; quarantined under godot/_quarantine/. This scene keeps the project runnable on
; mock-up primitives while the art is rebuilt and Path A is developed.
; The five LevelZones markers are the Path A spine (ADR 0006 / spec §4) — kept so
; the stagehand baker can promote them to PressureZones. uid preserved for project.godot.

